Postmark,is,an,email,delivery,service,for,web,apps,The,Spamcheck,API,gives,developers,a,programmatic,interface,to,the,spam,filter,tool,SpamAssassin,The,API,can,be,used,by,an,application,to,pre,or,post,process,email,content,It,helps,to,filter,out,junk,and,prevent,clutter,within,a,database,or,application,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON